<div type="apparatus">
<head>Apparatus</head>
<p>l. 13. The cutter wrote ΑΑΑ and then attempted to erase the bar of the second alpha; at the end of the line he wrote ΕΖΗΡΗΜΕΝΗΣ.</p>
